    <para styleclass="Heading2">Per-CPU slot offset keys (AARM Table 26-4)</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The slot stride is 0x280 (640 bytes): the AARM fields end at Cycle Counter Frequency (+624, last byte +631), padded to an octaword. This matches the live DS20 SRM. The five fields at +592..+624 were previously hidden in an opaque filler, and an in-slot DSRDB had inflated the slot to 0x400 (corrected 2026-06-29).</para>
